parameters:
Wow... It's become so beautiful. Before, it was
all worn out in various places.

The stairs are no longer uneven, making it easier
to walk. And the dirt on the approach has been
cleaned off too.

...I feel like there are more unnecessary guardian
dogs, but let's put that aside for now.

You said you were waiting, but I can't find you
anywhere...
You came at a good time, Ayako!
Geez!! Please don't surprise me like that!!

Hahaha!! It's been a while, so I had to surprise
you!
I don't need that kind of thing!!
Sigh... I was really worried, you know.

You suddenly disappeared and didn't respond at all
when I called you in my heart... Where were you
and what were you doing...?

While I'm working on the company, the barrier
weakens.

If that happens, bad energy will start coming in
again, so I've been running around to seal the
barrier.

It's like continuously repairing a leaky roof made
of paper in the pouring rain. Sanzuru was
extraordinary.

But!! Look at the result of my efforts!! It shines
just like it did when it was first built!!

And with the leftover money, I even bought some
guardian dogs to liven things up!
(So it was Rei-san's preference after all...)

All of this is thanks to your help. I'm truly
grateful.

It's okay. Did I manage to repay the favor a
little with this?
Well then, I must give you a reward for that.

Oh, that's right. Yes, yes, what kind of thing are
you going to give me next?

Is it something like winning drinks easily from
vending machines? Or finding lost items quickly?
You don't have to go out of your way to do
something amazing...

Slowing down aging, spontaneous combustion from
hands, reading people's minds, becoming invisible,
healing wounds, hypnosis, clairvoyance,
telekinesis, physical enhancement, increasing
vitality... and various other things.

W-What, suddenly amazing abilities!? And so many
of them!? W-What's going on?!

I will give you half of my spiritual power. I can
do at least that much.

Eh...? Are you sure it's okay for you to give me
your recovered spiritual power, Rei-san?

If I share my spiritual power, naturally my own
power will greatly decrease. It would cause a lot
of trouble.

....Before we talk about that, let me tell you the
conditions for granting you spiritual power first.

And the condition is, I want you to become my
substitute guardian!

That's right, if you can protect the barrier as a
guardian, I will be able to leave this place.

Eh?! Rei-san, are you planning to go somewhere?
It's so lonely after we've become close...

And... me as the guardian? I don't know what I
should do...

There must be a reason, right? I want you to
explain it to me...

That's right, there are things I must apologize to
you for as well.

Feel free to ask me anything. I'll do my best to
answer.

(And before that, you were talking about our
bloodline...)

(Alright, I'll ask you everything that's been on
my mind)

Well, I've answered everything I can answer. There
are no more secrets! It's only fair.

Everything that I have been hiding until now... my
power, bloodline, and what lies ahead as a
guardian...

Please carefully consider everything and decide
from your true feelings.

(Protecting this region is a huge
responsibility... I wonder if I'm really capable
of it...?)

(But, the power that Rei-san gives is incredibly
attractive...)

(If Haru-kun is also here, and if I can stay young
and healthy, it would be very reassuring...)

(And being able to use psychic powers... Being
able to do something so amazing sounds fun...)
...It seems like a decision has been made.

I...! I will become the guardian in place of Rei-
san.

Yes, I have some concerns, but I really like this
town and the excitement of being able to use
various psychic powers.

Besides, I want Rei-san to do things that she
likes too.
Hehehe... Blood really can't be denied, huh?

Very well...! Let us form a contract here and
perform the ritual to share our spiritual power...
.....Before that, this person is in the way.

Well? How do you like my esteemed countenance?
Look, look~ It's beautiful and even renders one
speechless.

...No, I mean, you can take off that mask-like
thing, right?
Just kidding, you're really cute, Rei-san.

That's right, that's right!! I'm super popular,
you know!! Hahaha!
Hehe, being with Rei-san is really fun after all.

Well, even though it was only for a short while, I
didn't get bored at all being with you.

...Thank you for taking care of me, Ayako. And
thank you for listening to my selfishness.
Me too. Thank you very much.

Alright!! Then let's begin the ritual of splitting
the spirits, shall we?!

Yes! Then, let's drink the super spiritual sake
that blends the semen of men with the morning
essence of my first squeeze, and then...

Man: This year, I hope I can get a girlfriend...!
This year, I hope I can finally graduate from
being a virgin...!

my luck in love...!

what the hell... sigh... My love luck isn't

The fact that you got rejected by a girl and

do...?!
